    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.poster.avif?t=1754408746\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.webm?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.mp4?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术类Roguelike卡组构建游戏，基于能力的战斗，依靠卡牌之间的联动。构建一副强大的卡组来支持你的英雄。使用各种能力消灭成群的敌人。从几乎无穷无尽的组合卡牌中发现强大的连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.poster.avif?t=1754408746\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.webm?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.mp4?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由卡牌支持的能力</strong>：英雄拥有3种需要法力值的能力。卡牌可以生成法力值、强化能力并治疗英雄。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于范围效果的战斗</strong>：大范围能力的伤害较低，高伤害能力的范围较小。巧妙地安排它们的使用顺序！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无惩罚的尝试</strong>：你可以撤销当前回合所做的一切操作。尝试不同的方法而不会受到任何惩罚。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组合卡牌</strong>：通过可互换的状态和循环机制组合，创造出几乎无穷无尽的卡牌种类。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.poster.avif?t=1754408746\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.webm?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.mp4?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Forestygian》目前拥有：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7</strong>位英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>54</strong>个敌人（20种敌人类型）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>52</strong>个卡牌循环（加上1个默认的小循环——药剂）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>38</strong>种状态效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >52 * 38 = <strong>1976</strong>张由循环和状态组合而成的卡牌（外加2张药剂卡）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.poster.avif?t=1754408746\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.webm?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138490/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.mp4?t=1754408746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
